{"tid":913364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒大師生Google賬戶癱瘓16小時","createTime":"2018-11-23T10:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T11:06:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95aff6c6bb81f1c3728292e3fb2ff89ce3348cc4","tid":913364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552566&d=AQftnGCaSe8XZIqBl4ISuTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=eee5e5fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181123%2F20552566&h=76216daf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181123/20552566</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月23日 <br />\n<br />\n恒大師生Google賬戶癱瘓16小時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181123/large/23la5p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181123%2Flarge%2F23la5p41.jpg&h=ef09eebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恒大所有師生的Gmail電郵賬戶前晚突遭關閉。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港恒生大學所有師生的Gmail電郵賬戶前晚突遭關閉。校方向學生發出的通告指出，Google疑校方的電郵戶口遭黑客入侵，連續寄出垃圾電郵，因而自動停止運作，Google Drive的功能亦受影響，直至昨早才恢復正常。Google其後再回應解釋，因最近啟動新的機制，防止高風險的群組濫發電郵，卻錯誤影響恒生大學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle換新機制出事<br />\n<br />\n香港恒生大學的Gmail電郵賬戶，前晚約7時半遭關閉，Google Drive功能受影響，導致同學文件、功課均不能取存。直至昨早11時30分，恒大所有Google賬戶才回復正常運作。校方對學生指，由於不少老師及同學均會用Google Drive下載文件，擔心會嚴重影響上課及工作，呼籲各位老師同學互相幫忙，日後不應過度依賴Google。<br />\n<br />\n本報向恒大查詢事件，校方回覆指，目前確認學校的資訊系統全部安全，個別用戶的戶口沒有不正常表現，以及沒有任何遺失數據的報告。而Google就解釋，因最近啟動了一個新的機制，防止高風險的群組濫發電郵，卻錯誤影響了香港恒生大學，Google支援中心已就此向恒大表示歉意，承諾會改善機制，不容許同類事件再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n近期大型機構接連發生黑客入侵事件，惹來驚弓之鳥。最為矚目是國泰航空10月24日公佈940萬名乘客資料被入侵。<br />\n<br />\n■記者區嘉儀  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nSPACE注資2.4億元凍過水<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n國產電動巴續航力不足退回廠方"},{"pid":"7f7361a928dcbcf4b530f99af431eed528d3544f","tid":913364,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9623bb6daafa74fb0f700ee7b595d5df093f4741","tid":913364,"uid":177561,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"邊到有人仲用google drive㗎? <br />\n係都用baidu云啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e4af199c1fa01102ec3829ab71ed6337291560","tid":913364,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T11:06:01.000Z","msg":"Google -&gt; Office 365"}]}